{"tid":2189394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[自煮研發啦仆街] 美國傳研制裁中芯國際 納入貿易黑名單","createTime":"2020-09-05T00:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T02:47:31.000Z","uid":108201,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d930b333604958c92492fb3d76a5d741cd00d79e","tid":2189394,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"路透報道，美國考慮將中芯(00981)納入貿易制裁黑名單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道引述美國國防部發言人稱，五角大樓與其他部門正在考慮，是否把這間中國最大晶片廠商納入黑名單。一旦納入黑名單，美國企業與中芯進行交易，必須事先得到美國商務部授予特別許可。<br />\n<br />\n這名華府官員沒有提及制裁中芯的原因，另一名官員指出，<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">中芯與解放軍之間的關係成為關注重點。</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國的貿易黑名單列出至少275間中資企業，當中包括華為、中興(00763)等。<br />\n<br />\n來源：信報"},{"pid":"08339da8d00c95186ba362dd5961285e36763252","tid":2189394,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"[內幕交易？]中芯國際（0981）遭到股東減持。據銷售文件顯示，中芯於今日收市後，以每股23.62至24.6元配售1.65億股中芯舊股，套現最多5.24億美元（約40.87億元），下限價較今日收市價折讓4%，上限價則與今日收市價無折讓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n銷售文件指出，配售股份的股東為Xinxin （Hong Kong）Capital，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">為多間國企旗下集成電路基金持有。</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66709f839f9f9b432dcf5a3002b98a5263a5f839","tid":2189394,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86788c46a50228be5fac229e7b77455ca72634d0","tid":2189394,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4350ec6688885a1d15585